This approach is especially useful when working with larger CSV files that would potentially exhaust a machine’s memory if Import-Csv were used. I have employed a similar technique to quickly find duplicates in large CSV files, and once identified over 9,000 duplicates within a million row CSV in only 6.4 seconds.

